  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This Adversary gains the ability to control their anger and use it to protect themself. As a free action, this adversary may clear itself of up to a number of Berserk ranks it has equal to half it's Proficiency Bonus. For each rank of Berserk cleared, this adversary gains 10 temporary hit points for the next minute. If a creature besides you were to clear ranks of Berserk, you still gain temporary hit points.</p>",
